    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in truly mint condition and has been meticulously maintained to showroom standards. The exterior paint is flawless with no chips, scratches, or dents, and the interior remains in pristine, like-new condition with no signs of wear on the upholstery or controls. Mechanically, the car performs perfectly, with a smooth engine, crisp shifting, and all electronic features functioning exactly as they did the day it rolled off the lot. A buyer can expect a vehicle that requires absolutely no immediate investment or repairs, offering a driving experience that is indistinguishable from a brand-new car.",
