    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "This is a rare opportunity to own a truly collector-grade vehicle that looks and drives exactly as it did the day it left the showroom. Meticulously maintained and stored in a climate-controlled garage, the exterior boasts a deep, mirror-like finish protected by a professional ceramic coating, with absolutely zero chips, dings, or swirls. Inside, the cabin remains in pristine condition; the premium leather seats show no signs of wear, the original factory scent lingers, and every electronic component functions flawlessly. Mechanically, the car is in impeccable order, backed by a comprehensive service history and exceptionally low original miles. It comes complete with both sets of keys, the original owner\u2019s manuals, and a clean title. This is a time capsule for the discerning enthusiast who demands perfection.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
